This very spacious home overlooks downtown Bremerton just  5minutes away from Naval Base , shopping and Ferry! Upstairs we have a Master Bedroom with an on-suite bathroom and walk-in closet, 2 secondary bedrooms, laundry, and another full bath. VA ASSUMABLE INTEREST RATE AT 2.5%...
